Author: DesperateLyingFox
Text: me too. yesterday someone took a picture of me. I know I gained a lot actually... but Apparently I didnt know how I looked at all. That Woman on the picture looks different than what I see in the mirror.  And I looked even worse in the picture... like, is that what people see?  first day in over three months that I didnt binged. I am so ashamed of myself. I look hideous
